title: #92Noon! Walz/Thibodeau/Leber/Krawczynski/Hersch
description: The Wolves join the Wild in the playoffs! Wes Walz talks about the Wild's L, Timberwolves Head Coach Tom Thibodeau talks about his team ending the 14-year drought, Ben Leber is in studio for NFL Draft discussion, The Athletic's Jon Krawczynski talks about finally making it into the postseason and the NHL Network's Jamie Hersch talks about the Stanley Cup Playoffs!
